Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I select 'Female' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'MRI pelvic floor' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
Then I go to Page 08 of Pelvic MRI
And I click on 'Finding' radio button
And dropdown below 'Finding' is enabled

When I select 'Rectum carcinoma' from the dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is preselected

And 'Upper third' checkbox is enabled
And 'Middle third' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lower third' checkbox is enabled

And 'Distance to the pectinate/dentate line' checkbox is enabled

And 'Circular' radio button is enabled
And 'Location according to SSL' radio button is enabled

And 'Maximum tumour diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Maximum CC-Expansion' input field is enabled

And 'Ulcerating' radio button is enabled
And 'Polypoid' radio button is enabled
And 'Signet ring cell tumor' radio button is enabled

And 'High T2w signal intensity, mucinous' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Upper third' checkbox
Then 'Peritoneal fold infiltration' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Middle third' checkbox
Then 'Peritoneal fold infiltration' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Distance to the pectinate/dentate line' checkbox
Then the input field below is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field
Then the numner is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field
Then the numner is accepted

When I select 'Lower third' checkbox
Then 'Above' radio button is enabled
And 'Below/at same height' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Above' radio button
Then input field below is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field
Then the numner is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field
Then the numner is accepted

When I select 'Below/at same height'  radio button
Then 'Infiltration of the internal anal sphincter' checkbox is enabled
And 'Infiltration of the external anal sphincter' checkbox is enabled
And 'Infiltration of the levator ani muscle' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Location according to SSL' radio button
Then dropdown below is enabled

When I click on any option from the dropdown
Then an option is selected

When I enter '1' in the input field 'Maximum tumour diameter'
Then the numner is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field 'Maximum tumour diameter'
Then the numner is accepted

When I enter '1' in the input field 'Maximum CC-Expansion'
Then the numner is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field 'Maximum CC-Expansion'
Then the numner is accepted

